	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>My hat! Not the hat!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_DEFEATED_2">
			<Text>I didn't see this coming!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>This is our dirt, we got here first! Stop taking our land!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>PuddingHead: I got it, crops on carts! So when they arrive they're fully grown![NEWLINE]Smart Cookie: Chancellor, it looks like we have guests.[NEWLINE]Puddinghead: Oh, Hi! Welcome to Dirtville![NEWLINE]Smart Cookie: Earth...[NEWLINE]Puddinghead: Earth! I hope we can work together, oh I got it! Shovelnoculars! So you can see what your digging!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>I knew that twitch ment something. What do you want?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Puddinghead: Oh hi! I'm real busy coming up with brillent ideas for our farms.[NEWLINE]Smart Cookie: Sigh.[NEWLINE]Puddinghead: What do you need?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Oh hi! Super nice seeing you!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>Puddinghead: Hmpf, you think I don't see what you're doing. You see this? This is my serious face.[NEWLINE]Smart Cookie: Sigh, she is being serious.[NEWLINE]Puddinghead: Well duh, you don't have to be a smart cookie to know that. Move your troops off our land!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>Hi! I was thinking that we should open our boarders! We got all kinds of neat stuff here!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1">
			<Text>Puddinghead: Er..Umm.........[NEWLINE]Smart Cookie: The Chancellor isn't really good at asking, but we could use your help.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PUDDING_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>Hi! We got lots of this stuff, and Smart Cookie tells me you have lots of stuff too! We should trade!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>


	

